<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_ee9374995cdb.aspx"><b>权舆</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonee9374995cdb">
<p>於我乎，夏屋渠渠，今也每食无余。于嗟乎，不承权舆！<br />於我乎，每食四簋，今也每食不饱。于嗟乎，不承权舆！</p>
